{"tid":951004,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"恒安邨惡男不滿「眼超超」打傷4男女 兩社工介入都捱打","createTime":"2018-12-22T03:39:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-22T11:05:56.000Z","uid":163529,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c9a637e1695f6784465baf64e01d8a80d3769e57","tid":951004,"uid":163529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T03:39:03.000Z","msg":"馬鞍山恒安邨商場，凌晨2時許，3男1女(32至36歲)與友人聊天，之後友人離開，其間當中一名男事主與另一名男子有眼神接觸，雙方「互睥」懷起衝突。<br />\n<br />\n稍後8名戴口罩男子撲出，向4男女襲擊，有人持木板作武器。其時湊巧有一名姓何(23歲)男社工及一名姓朱(29歲)女社工在場，他們見狀嘗試勸止，但反被襲擊，分別頭及手受傷。<br />\n<br />\n警方接報到場時，逞兇者已經四散，隨後將兩名社工及4名男女送院；警方正追緝逞兇者下落。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181222/59057958\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181222%2F59057958&d=pK2oF7PWZi%2FXTPe7b0RN5l0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=80e8bf82\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181222%2F59057958&h=2264503d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181222/59057958</a>"},{"pid":"ff0a1417c9b3968038567cccabcf6f38e391eaec","tid":951004,"uid":107364,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T03:40:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d670175408166b478ed2a34a5009c664931c5326","tid":951004,"uid":163529,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T03:40:45.000Z","msg":"社畜都照打<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8024dbb91f67e037de19838e59fa78a527258437","tid":951004,"uid":163529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T08:59:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c28ef362f7fd34aecc59748bd4b289dd140e673","tid":951004,"uid":32723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T09:16:42.000Z","msg":"打佢老母西啦<br />\n冬至迫人返屋企食飯"},{"pid":"01